implements NavigationView.OnNavigationItemSelectedListener

IMPORT_RQ - import request code

* onCreate
setNavigationItemSelectedListener on navigation view

* override onNavigationItemSelected(item: MenuItem)
using when(item.itemId) check the id and call appropriate MainPresenter method:
`Import database` - presenter.importSelected()
`Check for updates` - presenter.checkUpdatesSelected()
all others - presenter.navigateTo...

* importDialog - displays dialog to chose database tar file to import
- create intent ACTION_OPEN_DOCUMENT
- add category Intent.CATEGORY_OPENABLE
- set type to "application/x-tar"
- call startActivityForResult(intent, IMPORT_RQ)

* onActivityResult(requestCode: Int, resultCode: Int,Â resultData: Intent?)
- if resultCode is Activity.RESULT_OK i.e. user did chose tar file to import - proceed
- call presenter.checkTarFile(location)
where location is data retrieved from uri resultData

* noUpdates - displays a snackbar with message `No updates available.`
